00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,000
That's a lie.

354
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,000
I asked the proprietor to recommend the best.

355
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,000
At the same time crying poorhouse and making it plain

356
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,000
you wanted a cheap one.

357
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,000
I know your system.

358
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,000
By God I have to after this afternoon.

359
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:32,000
What about this afternoon?

360
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:36,000
Never mind now, we're talking about Mama.

361
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,000
I'm saying, no matter how you excuse yourself, you know damn

362
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,000
well you're stinginess is to blame.

