00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,000
You wanted us out of your way.

406
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,000
For that matter, if you want to judge her by what she says

407
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,000
when she's not in her right mind, if you'd never have been

