00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,000
born, she'd have never started--

409
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:24,000


410
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:25,000
Sure, Papa.

411
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,000
I know that's what she feels.

412
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:28,000
No, no, no, no, no, lad.

413
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:31,000


414
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:35,000
She loves you as dearly as a mother ever loved a son.

415
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:40,000


416
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:42,000
I only said that because you put me in such a God damn

417
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:45,000
rage, raking up the past and saying you hate me.

418
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:48,000
Well, I didn't mean it, Papa.

